snippet.textDisplay:
LOONA's random worldwide accomplishments (posting this again so some orbits have smth to read, feel free to add whatever, also Vivi NEEDS lines):
-FIRST Korean girl group (second girl group after Destiny’s Child & second kpop group after BTS) to get both a #1 single AND a #1 album on iTunes USA
-# is now the kpop girl group album with the most number 1s in iTunes (56 countries), beating Blackpink’s 2-year long record; this also makes LOONA the third highest-ranking kpop artist on iTunes after BTS and EXO
-‘365’ hit #1 on the Billboard World Digital Songs chart
-XX hit #1 in 34 countries (third kpop girl group album to top iTunes USA after Red Velvet & Twice); # made them the 2nd after RV to top the album chart twice
-first girl group to win the AAA popularity vote
-only musical group in history to have Jo Haseul as a leader! Congrats!
-Yves is Sunmi’s SUPER successful fan (srsly Sunmi likes every Yves post that people send her way)
-Haseul is Jo Sumi’s successful fan
-former 9MUSES’ Ryu Sera knows a lot about LOONA and supports them, noticed Yeojin’s ‘Dolls’ cover, and has given amazing advice to orbits about protecting LOONA in the industry. stan 9MUSES & support Sera’s Youtube channel <3
-acknowledged by Oh My Girl (Gowon's a successful fan), Hyomin, Martha Stewart, Charli XCX, slayyyter, BTS’ V, Soya, CLC’s Eunbin
-‘love4eva’ hand choreo done by Dreamcatcher’s Yoohyeon & Siyeon and A.C.E’s Jun (boy group w/ the most rights)
-collabed w/ Grimes
-played on TV in Brazil, Indonesia, Argentina, Netherlands; ‘Butterfly’ played in the background during the Portuguese version of Masked Singer
-exists in Overwatch according to Michael Chu (who’s a fan), Widowmaker’s canon fave member is Yves
-‘Eclipse’ was in NASA’s playlist
-LOONA songs played in H&M’s in US, France, Germany, Portugal, Belgium, etc.
-MTV EMA award for Best Korean Act; Yeojin’s the youngest EMA winner ever
-artistry acknowledged by Billboard, Teen Vogue, MTV (incl. MTV Brazil)
-LDN Noise wants to collab
-that Chuuves meme took OFF
-Janelle Monae wants to collab <3
-Soribada Performance Award 2019
-worked with NCT’s Cherry Bomb choreographer, who praised their skills; another SM choreographer wants them to cover Love Shot; Haechan watched their Cherry Bomb cover & said LOONA did it better (thanks lol)
-former SM CEO Lee Sooman reached out to LOONA to produce # after watching their Cherry Bomb cover, making them the first artist outside SM he’s worked with in his 25-year stint
-SNH48 (Shanghai-based girl group) covered ‘Butterfly’
-admired by Dreamnote, Busters, Lovelyz’ Jisoo, Pristin’s Kyla & Hinapia’s Eunwoo & Minkyeung, BVNDIT’s Jungwoo, BDC’s Junghwan, Conan Gray, Stray Kids’ Bang Chan, Noir’s Hoyeon, HKT48’s Rimika, SNH48’s Shen Mengyao, Bilal Hassani
-friends with WJSN, Itzy, DIA, Momoland, fromis_9, GWSN, Iz*one, Cherry Bullet, Astro, Elris, ANS’ Haena, Weki Meki’s Yoojung, cignature’s Jeewon and Good Day
-one of the first groups to explicitly acknowledge and provide support for LGBTQ fans <3 + tons of orbits at Pride events around the world (:
-also shout-out to the beautifully diverse women in ‘Butterfly’ (incl. positive Muslim representation)
-Hyunjin singlehandedly made that trashbag YG donate 50 million won toward ALS treatment by nominating him in the ice bucket challenge. One of history’s most iconic moments
-Chuu’s ‘biting heart’ went viral and is now done by all idols; Twice’s Dahyun & A.C.E’s Byeongkwan credited her as the official creator through ISAC & Pops in Seoul
-Han Hyunmin’s maybe a fan of Kim Lip lol?
-Chuu’s pic subtly referenced in a popular Korean webtoon
-Cocomong (animation) official social media posted about Kim Lip
-MTN’s Special Award for CF Star Rookies
-++ and XX sold 100K copies total for their debut
-first group to sell out merch at KCON 2019, plus LOONACON in general; collabed with a snack brand there
- trended on twitter #1 worldwide for the first time with LOONA_HIHIGH; AlwaysWithHaseul (<3) trended worldwide; JinsoulBlackHair, LOONAAA trended high in multiple countries; got their first Twitter Moment w/ Chuu’s # teaser; orbits originated the DESERVE meme too
-viral ‘Love Cherry Motion’ idol edits, and countless fantastic fan-edits w/ their discography (esp. ‘Girl Front’), incl. one Khalid noticed
-brand endorsement by a popular school uniform company
-one legendary winning team of a nationwide hacking competition in Indonesia was named ‘Stan LOOΠΔ!’; a legendary Filipino speed skater also said ‘stan loona’ during the SEA Games 2019 :P
-‘The Carol’ is the highest charting Korean Christmas song on iTunes USA
-Rod Breslau AKA Slasher recognized Olivia Hye as the top gamer girl ™ in the world

snippet.textDisplay:
Not an Orbit but I respect LOONA so much! And I noticed one thing in this badass mv: all closeup shots are on the face. No too tight or too short clothes and only visible in big shots (head to toe and surroundings). Short skirts dont count because they are part of the school uniform f.e. and just normal in korea.
This video is not for the so called male gaze. Its not about being badass and showing off how hot they are. LOONA basically say "Look at our faces and how we dance, dont objektify our bodies" and yet everything about them scream FIERCE QUEENS.
Very very well done and shoutout to all people who made this possible! If this wont be LOONAs first win, I dont know!
